JS 內建容器在 TS 怎麼型別化—學熟這節能寫 80% 業務 code。


### Array：兩種寫法

```typescript
// 寫法 1：type[]（推薦）
let nums: number[] = [1, 2, 3];

// 寫法 2：Array
let nums: Array = [1, 2, 3];

// 物件陣列
interface User {
    id: number;
    name: string;
}

const users: User[] = [
    { id: 1, name: "Alice" },
    { id: 2, name: "Bob" }
];

// 方法保持型別
const ids = users.map(u => u.id);              // number[]
const names = users.filter(u => u.id > 0).map(u => u.name);

// 找元素
const alice = users.find(u => u.name === "Alice");
// User | undefined（可能找不到、要檢查！）

if (alice) {
    console.log(alice.id);
}
```


### Tuple：固定結構

```typescript
type Coord = [x: number, y: number];

const point: Coord = [3, 4];
const [x, y] = point;

// 不同型別
type UserRow = [id: number, name: string, age: number];
const row: UserRow = [1, "Alice", 30];

// readonly tuple
const direction: readonly [number, number] = [0, 1];

// const 推導為 tuple（不是 array）
const arr = ["a", "b", "c"];               // string[]
const tuple = ["a", "b", "c"] as const;     // readonly ["a", "b", "c"]

// React useState
const [count, setCount] = useState(0);
// [number, (n: number) => void]
```


### Record：key-value 物件

```typescript
// Record = 所有 key 對應到某 V

// dictionary 風格
const scores: Record = {
    alice: 95,
    bob: 87
};

scores.dave = 91;

// 限制 key
type Role = "admin" | "editor" | "viewer";

const permissions: Record = {
    admin: ["read", "write", "delete"],
    editor: ["read", "write"],
    viewer: ["read"]
};

permissions.admin;       // string[]
permissions.other;       // ❌ 沒這 key
```


### Map：runtime 動態 key

```typescript
const cache = new Map();

cache.set("alice", { id: 1, name: "Alice" });
cache.set("bob", { id: 2, name: "Bob" });

const alice = cache.get("alice");   // User | undefined
cache.has("alice");                  // true
cache.delete("alice");
cache.size;                          // 1

// 跑 Map
for (const [key, user] of cache) {
    console.log(key, user.name);
}

// 比 object 強：
// 1. key 能是任何型別
// 2. 維持插入順序
// 3. 有 size / .has / .clear

// 計次範例
const counts = new Map();
for (const word of ["a", "b", "a", "c", "a"]) {
    counts.set(word, (counts.get(word) ?? 0) + 1);
}
```


### Set：不重複集合

```typescript
const tags = new Set();
tags.add("js");
tags.add("ts");
tags.add("js");   // 重複、不加

tags.has("js");        // true
tags.size;             // 2

// 去重陣列
const items = [1, 2, 3, 1, 2, 3];
const unique = [...new Set(items)];   // [1, 2, 3]

// 集合運算
const a = new Set([1, 2, 3, 4]);
const b = new Set([3, 4, 5, 6]);

// 聯集
const union = new Set([...a, ...b]);

// 交集
const intersection = new Set([...a].filter(x => b.has(x)));

// 差集
const diff = new Set([...a].filter(x => !b.has(x)));
```


### 實戰：完整資料結構

```typescript
// 購物車系統

interface Product {
    id: string;
    name: string;
    price: number;
}

interface CartItem {
    product: Product;
    quantity: number;
}

interface Cart {
    items: CartItem[];
    appliedCoupons: Set;
    discounts: Map;
    total: number;
}

function calculateTotal(cart: Cart): number {
    let total = cart.items.reduce(
        (sum, item) => sum + item.product.price * item.quantity,
        0
    );

    for (const discount of cart.discounts.values()) {
        total -= discount;
    }

    return Math.max(0, total);
}

// 統計：用 Record
type CategoryStats = Record;

const stats: CategoryStats = {
    "electronics": { totalSales: 50000, productCount: 30 },
    "books": { totalSales: 12000, productCount: 200 }
};
```


**☕ 用人話講**

4 個容器：(1) **Array**—順序資料 (2) **Tuple**—固定結構（useState 用） (3) **Record**—編譯時固定 key 的物件 (4) **Map**—runtime 動態 key (5) **Set**—不重複。**選擇**：固定 key 用 Record、動態用 Map、去重用 Set。

